Cold Stores slips on profit - taking . Shares of Ceylon Cold Stores Ltd dropped sharply on Thursday by 5 . 3 pct or ten rupees to 180 on retail profit - taking , brokers said . " Retail investors are taking profits after the high gains made by the share , " said Alastair Corera of Forbes & Walker Stock Brokers . Cold Stores produces and markets frozen foods and bottled drinks and is a subsidiary of John Keells Holdings Ltd . - - - Colombo newsroom ( 941 ) 434319 
